description: The 94 Shiki Senjutsu Hokou Sentouki Shiranui Ichigata Hei was deployed to the Yukon Base in Alaska under Project PROMINENCE as a test machine, gradually receiving upgrades and refinements with American hardware into the XFJ-01a Shiranui Second Phase 1.
name: 94 Shiki Senjutsu Hokou Sentouki Shiranui Ichigata Hei
